  <thing id="manPWCpyC1" name="Copycat Cut" description="With a slight shift of your stance you mimic an attack you’ve witnessed in the last few seconds of combat. When you initiate this strike, make a melee attack. If you hit, you deal an additional 1d6 points of damage and you can choose to use the result of any attack roll made by that opponent in his next turn for one of your attack rolls in your next turn. If you strike that opponent with his own attack roll, you deal an additional 3d4 points of damage. This maneuver does not threaten or confirm critical hits." compset="PWManuever" summary="Strike – Make a melee attack for an additional 1d6 damage, copy struck opponent’s attack roll on your next attack." uniqueness="useronce">
